site.title: Microsoft Azure API Management - developer portal
site.description: Discover APIs, learn how to use them, try them out interactively, and sign up to acquire keys.
site.author: Microsoft Azure API Management

nodes.text: Transform ideas into reality with our APIs
Our API Developer Portal offers the tools you need to explore, test, and integrate APIs with ease. Start building today.
Learn how to get started with our APIs and explore our catalog to find the perfect API for your needs.
Products in the developer portal encompass one or more APIs. Subscribe to a product to get access to utilize the APIs.
Need help? Our API admin team is here for you. Reach out to us for any questions or assistance with our APIs.
